metadata.name: PIXEL BUNNY #1
metadata.description: Blasé Bunny Pixel is a collection of 50 unique NFTs that are created by the anonymous team of artists behind the Blasé Bunny Studio. This will be a beta launch open to our dear friends and strategic partners. The Pixel style is considered a legacy version that will be only issued once.  Each Blasé Bunny Pixel NFT you own will allow you to access certain exclusive membership benefits, such as access to the Underground Blasé Bunny Common Room, Future NFT giveaways, products discount ranging from artworks to wearables and the list goes on.
